cl-mempool
==========

Standalone transaction mempool library extracted from CLPIC
(Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain)

Original Source: https://github.com/clpic/clpic
Extracted Module: src/mempool/

This is a pure Common Lisp implementation with zero external dependencies.
The code is derived from CLPIC's transaction pool implementation, adapted
for standalone use.

Features derived from:
- src/mempool/v2/ - Pool V2 architecture, EIP-1559/4844 support
- src/mempool/pending/ - Pending pool with nonce tracking
- src/mempool/relay-policy.lisp - RBF and relay policies

